venue.name: Nunziato Dog Park

item.description:
Time for another Shiba meetup (hoping that the rain forecast for Saturday has tapered off by Sunday morning).

We're trying out a new location for this meetup - the "Nunziato Off-Leash Recreational Area" in Somerville; hopefully it won't be as muddy as our usual venues in Medford or Sharon.

adam
